<HH> ============= Screen: The roommate's reply ======================== </HH>

<Markdown id="roommate_response">
## Annie's roommate's email:

Hey!

I just wanted to thank you and your friends for helping me out
with the bedtime situation!

I tried the positive reinforcement technique you all suggested,
and it actually worked!

It took me a while to figure out the perfect reinforcement. He loves
Paw Patrol, so I started giving him Paw Patrol stickers to reinforce him
going to bed on time. I gave him one sticker for getting into bed and
told him that I would leave more stickers for his mom to give him in
the morning, IF he stayed in bed and went to sleep. 😊

So far, he has gone to bed without a fuss three nights in a row!

Please tell everyone I really appreciate their ideas! Y'all are lifesavers!
</Markdown>


